== 背景 ==
{{main|2013年－2014年泰國反政府示威}}
[[2011年泰國大選|2011年泰國大選]]，[[英樂·欽那瓦|盈拉·欽那瓦]]與[[为泰党|为泰党]]（PTP）獲得了壓倒性勝利，英拉組成新政府並擔任總理。2013年11月，[[泰國民主黨|民主黨]]籍的[[素貼·特素班|素貼·特素班]]為領袖，與數個團體組成了{{link-en|人民民主改革委員會|People's Democratic Reform Committee}}（PDRC），策動了反政府的示威騷亂，素貼並自任該委員會秘書長，期間曾與親政府的[[反獨裁民主聯盟|泰國紅衫軍]]發生多起衝突，當中亦有人死傷。<ref>{{cite web |title = Why is Thailand under military rule? |publisher = BBC |date = 2014-05-22 |accessdate = 2014-05-23 |url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-25149484 |archive-date = 2014-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140523023042/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-25149484 |dead-url = no }}{{en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title = Death toll in Thai anti-gov't protests reaches four, dozens injured |publisher = The Voice of Russia |date = 2014-02-18 |accessdate = 2014-05-23 |url = http://voiceofrussia.com/news/2014_02_18/Death-toll-in-Thai-anti-govt-protests-reaches-four-dozens-injured-5990/ |archive-date = 2014-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140523230243/http://voiceofrussia.com/news/2014_02_18/Death-toll-in-Thai-anti-govt-protests-reaches-four-dozens-injured-5990/ |dead-url = no }}{{en}}</ref>

2013年12月，英拉解散[[泰國眾議院|眾議院]]，並訂於2014年2月2日舉行大選。但由反政府示威者的阻擾及民主黨杯葛選舉，大選的各地投票並未能在同一天完成，部分選區的議員無法產生，故軍方控制的[[泰國憲法法院|泰國憲法法院]]在2014年3月21日以「違憲」為由判決選舉「無效」。<ref>{{cite web |title = Constitutional Court nullifies Feb 2 election |url = http://www.nationmultimedia.com/breakingnews/Constitutional-Court-nullifies-Feb-2-election-30229741.html |work = The Nation |date = 2014-03-21 |accessdate = 2014-05-22 |archive-date = 2014-03-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140324033311/http://www.nationmultimedia.com/breakingnews/Constitutional-Court-nullifies-Feb-2-election-30229741.html |dead-url = no }}{{en}}</ref>

2014年5月7日，受軍方控制的泰國憲法法院再解除英拉與{{link-en|盈拉·欽那瓦內閣|Yingluck cabinet|多個內閣首長}}職務。<ref>{{cite news|title=Yingluck, 9 ministers removed from office|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/politics/408549/yingluck-9-ministers-removed-from-office|accessdate=22 May 2014|newspaper=Bangkokpost|date=7 may 2014}}{{en}}</ref><ref name = "ylremoval">{{cite web |title = อวสาน "ยิ่งลักษณ์"พ่วง รมต. ! "ศาล รธน.ฟันสิ้นสุดความเป็นรมต.ย้าย "ถวิล" มิชอบใช้อำนาจเอื้อ "เพรียวพันธ์" |trans_title = The end of Yingluck and her fellow ministers, charter court removed them over abuse of power to transfer Thawin in favour of Priewpan |url = http://www.manager.co.th/Politics/ViewNews.aspx?NewsID=9570000050542 |language = th |date = 2014-05-07 |accessdate = 2014-05-07 |publisher = Manager |archive-date = 2014-05-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140508042820/http://www.manager.co.th/Politics/ViewNews.aspx?NewsID=9570000050542 |dead-url = no }}</ref> 其後，由副總理兼商務部長的[[尼瓦塔隆·汶颂派讪|尼瓦塔隆·汶颂派讪]]被選為[[看守政府|看守政府]]總理以取代英拉，但騷亂仍在持續。<ref>{{cite web |title = Yingluck removed, Niwatthamrong acting PM |url = http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/local/408561/yingluck-removed-niwatthamrong-acting-pm |date = 2014-05-07 |accessdate = 2014-05-07 |publisher = Bangkok Post }}{{en}}</ref>

== 政變之前 ==
=== 戒嚴 ===
[[File:Prayuth_Jan-ocha_2010-06-17_Cropped.jpg|缩略图]]2010年資料照]]
2014年5月20日，時任[[泰國皇家陸軍|泰國皇家陸軍]]（RTA）總司令的巴育將軍發動政變，宣布根據《[[1914年泰國戒嚴法|1914年泰國戒嚴法]]》，自當地時間凌晨三時起全國戒嚴。他透過電視發表演說時聲稱，軍方實行戒嚴，是為「使各地持續的暴力抗議行為盡早落幕並恢復和平」。<ref>{{cite web | title = ผบ.ทบ. ลงนามประกาศกฎอัยการศึกทั่วประเทศ มีผลวันนี้ 03.00 น. | trans_title = RTA commander declares martial law nationwide, effective from today, 03:00 hrs | url = http://www.manager.co.th/Politics/ViewNews.aspx?NewsID=9570000055656 | date = 2014-05-20 | accessdate = 2014-05-20 | language = th | publisher = Manager | archive-date = 2014-05-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140520002030/http://www.manager.co.th/Politics/ViewNews.aspx?NewsID=9570000055656 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Thailand's army declares martial law, says not a coup|url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/101668507|accessdate=2014-05-22|newspaper=CNBC|date=2014-05-19|archive-date=2014-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140522195738/http://www.cnbc.com/id/101668507|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>

戒嚴後，巴育將軍非法解散看守政府成立的警務機構：和平秩序行政中心（Centre for Administration of Peace and Order，CAPO），然後自組了{{link-th|「維持和平與秩序指揮部」|กองอำนวยการรักษาความสงบเรียบร้อย}}（Peace and Order Maintaining Command，POMC），並自任指揮官。

