=== 五方會談 ===
[[File:Thai-coup-detat-2014-social-media-banner.jpg|thumb]]
在成立後兩天的5月22日，POMC曾召開與各方團體的會談。五方代表為：[[泰國總理|泰國看守政府總理]][[尼瓦塔隆·汶颂派讪|尼瓦塔隆·汶颂派讪]]、[[反獨裁民主聯盟|泰國紅衫軍]]、[[為泰黨|為泰黨]]、{{link-en|人民民主改革委員會|People's Democratic Reform Committee}}、[[民主黨_(泰國)|泰國民主黨]]。當中包含了[[素貼·特素班|素貼·特素班]]、{{link-en|乍度蓬|Jatuporn Prompan}}（Jatuporn Prompan）等人。<ref name="泰国第12次政变 全國宵禁"/>但參加者間爭持不下，且不同意採納彼此意見。<ref name = "NCPO">{{cite web | title = 'ประยุทธ์-เหล่าทัพ'แถลง'ควบคุมอำนาจรัฐ' | trans_title = Prayuth and military chiefs are controlling state powers | url = http://www.komchadluek.net/detail/20140522/185160.html | date = 2014-05-22 | accessdate = 2014-05-22 | language = th | publisher = Komchadluek | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140522161112/http://www.komchadluek.net/detail/20140522/185160.html | archive-date = 2014-05-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

此外，會談期間，{{link-en|泰國選舉委員會|Election Commission of Thailand}}曾要求看守政府辭職<ref>{{cite web | title = Thai military says it's taken over the country in a coup | publisher = CNN | date = 2014-05-22 | accessdate = 2014-05-22 | url = http://www.cnn.com/2014/05/22/world/asia/thailand-martial-law/index.html?hpt=hp_t2 | archive-date = 2014-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140522153606/http://www.cnn.com/2014/05/22/world/asia/thailand-martial-law/index.html?hpt=hp_t2 | dead-url = no }}{{en}}</ref>，但依照憲法規定，看守內閣必須留任。<ref name = "flee">{{cite web | title = นิวัฒน์ธำรงเผ่นก่อนถูกยึดอำนาจ | trans_title = Niwatthamrong fled before coup launched | url = http://www.posttoday.com/%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%87/296408/%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%92%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%98%E0%B8%B3%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%87%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%9C%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%81%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%96%E0%B8%B9%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%B6%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%B3%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%88 | language = th | publisher = Post Today | date = 2014-05-22 | accessdate = 2014-05-22 | archive-date = 2019-02-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190213043117/https://www.posttoday.com/%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%87/296408/%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%92%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%98%E0%B8%B3%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%87%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%9C%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%81%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%96%E0%B8%B9%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%B6%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%B3%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%88 | dead-url = no }}</ref>因《{{link-en|泰王國2007年憲法|2007 Constitution of Thailand}}》第181條規定，當眾議院全部解散時，內閣需保持運作，直至新內閣接手為止。<ref>{{cite web | title = Constitution of the Kingdom of Thailand 2007 (section 181) | author = Council of State of Thailand | publisher = Asian Legal Information Institute | year = 2007 | accessdate = 2014-05-22 | url = http://www.asianlii.org/th/legis/const/2007/1.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120515162053/http://www.asianlii.org/th/legis/const/2007/1.html | archivedate = 2012-05-15 }}{{en}}</ref>

